{"type": "article", "id": 16781, "title": "啊这些大象犀牛章鱼椅子，也太浮夸了", "description": "感觉来到了改装过的史前生物陈列室。好啦，我知道什么是史前生物，就是这么一说。", "date": "2015-10-29T18:09:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 13180, "name": "雕塑"}, {"id": 17985, "name": "仿真"}, {"id": 266, "name": "椅子"}, {"id": 17986, "name": "Maximo Riera"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 172, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703122442JXFxjcEOKgP74lLN.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t西班牙艺术家 Maximo Riera 带来了他的动物椅子系列，章鱼、海象、犀牛、大象、河马、鲸鱼全都背上了一个欧洲古典风格的座位。因为是在画廊展出，仿真的大块动物搭配现代建筑，颇有生物入侵的感觉。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031224344rHmMIUPTnkXzZS5.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"548\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122434WGRTstY4flaJbI2S.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"949\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.99894737\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122435KwuEFhx2InJYDjQz.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122435t1AkPEOVZYJbz7pa.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"523\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122436mUCgtRYMyTcbSw3E.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"633\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66631579\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122436jbQzP52l3wCkqMfn.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"824\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.00733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122437xFn3OZR76Xh9cuYC.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070312243714mdAuY9QNFOMiEs.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"633\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66631579\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122438uxKDOQGY3ScJnzR7.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"614\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122438psgmM798eWolnr4J.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"538\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65770171\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122439szW9XecD7kQAGPfV.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"556\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6797066\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122439UfxLNnaMFShzOi7P.jpg\" width=\"504\" height=\"650\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.28968254\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>每一个动物座椅都是高密度聚氨酯的材料做的，内部用铁来支撑，有弹性且能持久使用。为了确保精确，设计师从 3D 建模开始，然后进行人工切割，每一个都要花上大概 480 小时，换算成实际工作量达到了 9 周到 11 周。这个系列已经在不同的地方展出并持续更新，甚至可以售卖。</span><a href=\"http://maximoriera.com/animal-chair-collection/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是他的主页。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t不过，这些椅子都是重量级的，大象椅子甚至重达 125 千克，<span>算得上半个雕塑了。</span>恐怕更适合出现在酒店之类的场所（买一个镇镇场子就够了）。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122439uivMd1fPzRlyYoCm.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"534\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56210526\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122440pasuf19HLUzkTv2E.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"534\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56210526\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122440KRGJv2lA5trqBph3.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"534\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56210526\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122441scevTVgOm8XCrkAa.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"534\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56210526\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122441Hrl8LC3vhIt9ZmMn.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"534\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56210526\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144053dO61ZnglHRVGu2tz.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"637\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.67052632\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/art/maximo-riera-animal-chair-collection-new-edition-10-29-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">designboom</a>、<a href=\"http://maximoriera.com/gallery/\" target=\"_blank\">maximoriera</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}